author: Freya McClements
title: Coronavirus: Warning that 3,000 people could die in North over 20 weeks
description: 180 patients with virus would require ventilation and critical care beds – Minister
content:
Three thousand people could die of coronavirus in Northern Ireland in 20 weeks, according to the estimates by the Department of Health (DoH).
